{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.6","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.5","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.4"],"generated":true}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.14"]}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Migrating to 1.14"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" type is now officially "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"text":" isolated.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As the library prepares for Swift 6 we are in the process of updating the library’s APIs for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"sendability and isolation where appropriate, and doing so in a backwards compatible way. Prior","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to version 1.14 of the library the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"text":" type has only ever been meant to be used on the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"main thread, but that contract was not enforced in any major way. If a store was interacted with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"on a background thread a runtime warning would be emitted, but the compiler had no knowledge of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the type’s isolation."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That now changes in 1.14 where "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" is now officially ","type":"text"},{"code":"@MainActor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"-isolated. This has been","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"done in a way that should be 100% backwards compatible, and if you have problems please open a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"However, if you are using ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strict"}]},{"type":"text","text":" concurrency settings in your app, then there is one circumstance"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in which you may have a compilation error. If you are accessing the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store"},{"type":"text","text":" in a view method or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"property in Xcode <16, then you may have to mark that property as "},{"code":"@MainActor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"code":[" struct FeatureView: View {","   let store: StoreOf<Feature>"," ","   var body: some View {","     \/\/ ...","   }"," ","+  @MainActor","   var title: some View {","     Text(store.name)","   }"," }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"diff"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14"},"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/MigratingTo1.8":{"title":"Migrating to 1.8","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.8","role":"article","type":"topic","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","abstract":[{"text":"Update your code to make use of the new capabilities of the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Reducer()","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" macro, including automatic"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"fulfillment of requirements for destination reducers and path reducers.","type":"text"}]},"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture":{"title":"ComposableArchitecture","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Composable Architecture (TCA, for short) is a library for building applications in a consistent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and understandable way, with composition, testing, and ergonomics in mind. It can be used in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI, UIKit, and more, and on any Apple platform (iOS, macOS, tvOS, and watchOS)."}],"url":"\/documentation\/composablea